sequenceDiagram
    participant K8s
    participant GPU as GPU Nodes
    participant Riva as Riva Service (ASR/TTS)
    participant NIM as NIM Service (LLM)
    participant GW as Voice Gateway

    Note over K8s: Phase 3: Deployment (Helm Install)

    par Deploy Models
        K8s->>Riva: Schedule Pod
        Riva->>GPU: Alloc GPU
        Riva->>Riva: Download/Load Models (Heavy)
        
        K8s->>NIM: Schedule Pod
        NIM->>GPU: Alloc GPU
        NIM->>NIM: Download/Load Model (Heavy)
    end

    Note right of K8s: Gateway waits for Services

    K8s->>GW: Schedule Pod
    GW->>Riva: Connect (gRPC)
    GW->>NIM: Connect (HTTP/gRPC)
    
    Note over GW: Traffic Starts

